            <title>[FLUME-1867] There&apos;s no option to set hostname for HTTPSource</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLUME-1867</link>
                <project id="12311321" key="FLUME">Flume</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I&apos;d like to request the ability to specify a particular host (and thus a specific NIC) for HTTPSource so that user can choose to listen on one NIC or all NICs. Currently only the port number can be specified, not the hostname. Can we add a &apos;host&apos; prop to HttpSource?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
